entries.s_10: Thank you for finding my cards! And a happy Festival of Love to you!
entries.s_12: Can you help find my lost Festival of Love cards?
entries.s_14: I would be glad to help.
entries.s_16: Oh thank you! I lost them while wandering through Tyrena, Kaadara, or our Lake village. I had a complete set in a nice bundle, but they must've come loose.
entries.s_20: Oh, I see. Happy Festival of Love to you.
entries.s_22: Oh, thank you! Here take some of my Festival of Love Chak Hearts...it's the least I can do in return. Oh, and if you don't mind, come see me again tomorrow. I may need more cards!
entries.s_4: You found them! The entire set!!
entries.s_8: Please find my Festival of Love cards.
